data.description: Fabulous opportunity for home ownership in one of Gentry's newest neighborhoods. The split floor plan provides privacy for the owners. The owner's site boasts tray ceiling, double sinks, a whirlpool tub, and a huge walk-in closet. The three other bedrooms are found on the opposite side of the home. The second full bath is oversized with a linen closet. The eat-in kitchen with dark cabinets, granite counters, and pantry opens to the living room. Enjoy the fall weather on your deck- the backyard is fully fenced.
